      "created_at": "2024-04-29T12:33:40.587Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Update:<br>\nTurns out Suito can support bridge sensors. I needed to update my trainer\u2019s software in the \u201cUpgrado\u201d app from Elite. I can now bridge HR and cadence through the trainer!<br>\nUnfortunately, now I have lost power output from the trainer to my phone and connected cycling computer. I currently have a ticket in with Elite to try to resolve this issue. Returning the trainer is always an option, I guess.</p>",
