      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/35a633/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2024-05-23T18:46:38.430Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Final Update:<br>\nAfter weeks of back and forth, no solution has been found. The trainer was working before a software update, after the update the trainer lost the ability to transmit power. Manufacturer sent a replacement part, after that did not fix the issue I received the \u201cNot our problem\u201d email. Fortunately, Amazon customer service was able to get the seller to take back the defective unit; I was able to get a full refund. I am <strong>not</strong> happy at all with Elite and this Elite Suito. I will be going with a different brand and cannot recommend this trainer at all.<br>\nOn a side note, any suggestions for a budget minded direct drive smart trainer that is not an Elite trainer?<br>\nty.</p>",
